task.summary: IDEA project settings and some solved code style issues.
Mainly documentation on creation/conversion of documents from raw data. Some minor changes regarding the code conventions.
A complete dialogue as example for the documentation.
Deleted settings of formerly used IDEs.
Refactored the package structure. Common code and code which is specific for the analysis of BoRis data are clearly separated.
Added rank order distance as new measure. However, its usage must be still implemented.
- implemented rank order distance (must be used in the cross validation) - wrote unit tests for all measures - wrote unit test for rank order distance
A lot of cleaning regarding smoothing and n-gram model creation.
- more unit tests - creation of rank based models
- outdated scripts are deleted - histogram script is updated
- outdated scripts are deleted - histogram script is updated
Prepared for a complete evaluation, using all criteria.
